snippet.title: Blood Card 2 Dark Mist Gameplay (PC Game)
snippet.description:
Dark Mist is a card game that combines elements of the roguelike deckbuilder genre with enemies that appear in waves. Defeat monsters and level up during battle to keep yourself going.
Support the developer by purchasing the game on steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/968760/Blood_Card_2_Dark_Mist/
